nodes.text: This Agri-Corps boat was commissioned by Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn in 44 BBY, in order to save Obi-Wan Kenobi from the deepsea mines of Bandomeer. Qui-Gon procured the boat from a Meerian, RonTha, who worked for Agri-Corps Enrichment Zone. Qui-Gon was successful in rescuing Obi-Wan, and they tied the boat up at the Offworld loading dock.
